native.query:
SELECT DISTINCT
    "bnpl_ledger"."partner_name" AS "PARTNER_NAME",
    "bnpl_ledger"."customer_name" AS "CUSTOMER_NAME",
    "bnpl_ledger"."invoice_number" AS "INVOICE_NUMBER",
    "bnpl_ledger"."invoice_external_number" AS "INVOICE_EXTERNAL_NUMBER",
    "bnpl_ledger"."transaction_timestamp" AS "TRANSACTION_TIMESTAMP",
    "bnpl_ledger"."transaction_status" AS "TRANSACTION_STATUS",
    "bnpl_ledger"."bnpl_ledger_id" AS "PAYMENT_ID",
    "bnpl_ledger"."payment_trigger" AS "PAYMENT_TRIGGER",
    "bnpl_ledger"."payment_amount" AS "PAYMENT_AMOUNT",
    "bnpl_ledger"."payment_net_amount" AS "PAYMENT_NET_AMOUNT",
    "bnpl_ledger"."partner_id" AS "PARTNER_ID",
    "bnpl_ledger"."customer_id" AS "CUSTOMER_ID",
    "Svb Return Codes"."return_code_created_at" AS "Svb Return Codes__return_code_created_at",
    "Svb Return Codes"."return_code" AS "Svb Return Codes__return_code",
    "Svb Return Codes"."transaction_failure_reason" AS "Svb Return Codes__transaction_failure_reason"
FROM gold.bnpl_ledger AS "bnpl_ledger"
LEFT JOIN default.alt_svb_svb_responses AS "Svb Return Codes" ON "bnpl_ledger"."bnpl_ledger_id" = "Svb Return Codes"."id"
WHERE ("bnpl_ledger"."transaction_status" = 'chargeback') AND ("bnpl_ledger"."payment_method" = 'ach')
ORDER BY "Svb Return Codes"."return_code_created_at" DESC
LIMIT 1048575
